OL,4,CAgeing equipment puts Army 'at risk' -
OL,5,Creport
OL,6, The British Army is likely to find
OL,7, itself "outgunned" in any conflict with
OL,8, Russian forces, MPs have warned.
OL,10,FIn a damning report, the Commons
OL,11,FDefence Committee described efforts to
OL,12,Fmodernise the Army's fleet of Armoured
OL,13,FFighting Vehicles (AFV) as "woeful".
OL,15,FThe ageing and depleted fleet puts the
OL,16,FArmy at "serious risk" of being
OL,17,Foutmatched by adversaries, it states.
OL,19,FThe Ministry of Defence has promised
OL,20,F"an upgraded, digitised and networked
OL,21,Farmoured force to meet future threats".
